data.name: MediVisionX
data.description: About The "AI Health VIsion" repository is dedicated to analyzing various diseases using convolutional neural networks (CNN) and integrating the results into an Android application.

data.name: Content-Moderation-Tool
data.description: A web extension that blocks NSFW (Not Safe For Work) content on Internet in Realtime based on the age verification.

data.name: Anomaly-Behavior-Analysis-in-Financial-Transactions
data.description: This repository uses graph neural networks (GNNs) to analyze and detect anomalies in financial transactions, specifically fraudulent activities in credit card transactions.

data.name: ProteinViz
data.description: ProteinViz is a repository developed using Python and Flask for the 3D representation of proteins, facilitating advanced internal studies. This tool enables researchers and scientists to visualize protein structures in a three-dimensional space, aiding in the analysis and understanding of their properties and interactions.

data.name: Flutter-Graphology
data.description: Flutter-Graphology is a Flutter application designed for graphology enthusiasts and practitioners. It provides tools for analyzing handwriting and inferring personality traits using graphological techniques.

data.name: MINS
data.description: An efficient and robust multisensor-aided inertial navigation system with online calibration that is capable of fusing IMU, camera, LiDAR, GPS/GNSS, and wheel sensors. Use cases: VINS/VIO, GPS-INS, LINS/LIO, multi-sensor fusion for localization and mapping (SLAM). This repository also provides multi-sensor simulation and data.
